Running::Commentary version 0.000005

This module provides a single subroutine: run()
which is designed to be a more informative and
less error-prone replacement for the built-in system().


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


